query.querystring: SELECT species.Species, comnames.NameType, species.Genus, countref.C_Code FROM comnames, species, countref WHERE comnames.SpecCode=species.SpecCode AND comnames.C_Code=countref.C_Code AND comnames.ComName="Cuban cichlid"

SELECT species.SpecCode, species.Author, species.FBname, refrens.Author, refrens.Year, species.Comments, families.Family, families.FamilyOrder, families.Class, morphdat.AddChars, species.DemersPelag, species.SpeciesRefNo, species.AnaCat, species.PicPreferredName, picturesmain.autoctr, picturesmain.PicName, picturesmain.Entered, picturesmain.AuthName FROM species, refrens, morphdat, families, picturesmain WHERE species.SpeciesRefNo=refrens.RefNo AND species.SpecCode=morphdat.SpecCode AND species.FamCode=families.FamCode AND species.SpecCode =picturesmain.SpecCode AND (species.Genus="Porochilus" AND species.Species="obbesi")
SELECT species.Species, species.Author, families.Family FROM species, families WHERE species.FamCode=families.FamCode AND species.Genus="Barbus"
SELECT species.Author, species.Genus, families.Family FROM species, families WHERE species.FamCode=families.FamCode AND species.Species="rudolphi"

SELECT families.FamilyOrder, families.Class, families.Genera, families.Species, families.SpeciesCount,families.Marine, families.Brackish, families.Freshwater, families.Aquarium, families.Remark, families.Division, families.Activity, refrens.Author, refrens.Year, families.ReprGuild FROM families, refrens WHERE families.FamiliesRefNo=refrens.RefNo AND families.Family="Cyclopteridae"
SELECT species.Author, species.Species, species.Genus FROM species, families WHERE species.FamCode=families.FamCode AND families.Family="Centrogenyidae"
SELECT species.Author, species.Species, species.Genus FROM species, families WHERE species.FamCode=families.FamCode AND families.Family="Tetragonuridae"

SELECT species.Genus, species.Species, picturesmain.PicName, picturesmain.AuthName FROM fbapp.species, fbapp.picturesmain, fbapp.families WHERE species.SpecCode = picturesmain.SpecCode AND (species.FamCode =families.FamCode AND families.Family="Pangasiidae")

SELECT collaborators.Prename, collaborators.Surname, collaborators.Email, collaborators.WebPage, collaborators.FAX, collaborators.Institute, collaborators.Street, collaborators.City, collaborators.Country, collaborators.Comments, collaborators.Keywords, collaborators.Year FROM collaborators WHERE collaborators.Personnel=290

SELECT species.Genus, species.Species, picturesmain.AuthName, picturesmain.LifeStage FROM fbapp.species, fbapp.picturesmain WHERE species.SpecCode = picturesmain.SpecCode AND picturesmain.PicName="Lulem_u0.gif"

SELECT families.FamilyOrder, families.Family, species.Genus, species.Species, country.Status FROM fbapp.species, fbapp.country, fbapp.countref, fbapp.families WHERE species.SpecCode = country.SpecCode AND species.FamCode = families.FamCode AND country.C_Code=countref.C_Code AND countref.PAESE="Papua N Guin"

SELECT country.Status, country.Freshwater, country.Saltwater, country.Brackish, countref.Factbook FROM country, countref, species WHERE country.C_Code=countref.C_Code AND country.SpecCode=species.SpecCode AND species.Genus="Stethojulis" AND species.Species="terina" AND countref.PAESE="Guyana"

SELECT families.FamilyOrder , families.Family, species.Genus,species.Species, country.Status, comnames.ComName FROM families, species, comnames, countref, country WHERE country.C_Code=countref.C_Code AND species.FamCode=families.FamCode AND comnames.SpecCode=species.SpecCode AND country.SpecCode=species.SpecCode AND country.Freshwater=1 AND countref.PAESE="Easter I."

SELECT families.FamilyOrder , families.Family, species.Genus,species.Species, comnames.ComName FROM fbapp.families, fbapp.species, fbapp.comnames, fbapp.countref, fbapp.country WHERE country.C_Code=countref.C_Code AND species.FamCode = families.FamCode AND species.SpecCode=country.SpecCode AND species.SpecCode=comnames.SpecCode AND countref.PAESE="Hungary" AND country.Status="introduced"

SELECT families.FamilyOrder , families.Family, species.Genus,species.Species, comnames.ComName FROM fbapp.families, fbapp.species, fbapp.comnames, fbapp.countref, fbapp.country WHERE country.C_Code=countref.C_Code AND country.SpecCode=species.SpecCode AND comnames.SpecCode=species.SpecCode AND species.FamCode = families.FamCode AND countref.PAESE="Micronesia" AND country.Status="endemic"

SELECT families.FamilyOrder , families.Family, species.Genus,species.Species, country.Status, comnames.ComName, species.Dangerous FROM fbapp.families, fbapp.species, fbapp.comnames, fbapp.countref, fbapp.country WHERE countref.C_Code=country.C_Code AND country.SpecCode=species.SpecCode AND comnames.SpecCode=species.SpecCode AND species.FamCode = families.FamCode AND countref.PAESE="Denmark" AND species.DemersPelag="reef-associated"

SELECT families.FamilyOrder , families.Family, species.Genus,species.Species, country.Status, comnames.ComName, species.Dangerous FROM fbapp.families, fbapp.species, fbapp.comnames, fbapp.countref, fbapp.country WHERE countref.C_Code=country.C_Code AND comnames.SpecCode=species.SpecCode AND country.SpecCode=species.SpecCode AND species.FamCode = families.FamCode AND countref.PAESE="Tonga" AND species.DemersPelag="pelagic"

SELECT families.Family, families.FamilyOrder, species.Genus,species.Species, country.Status, comnames.ComName, species.GameFish, species.GameRef FROM fbapp.families, fbapp.species, fbapp.comnames, fbapp.countref, fbapp.country WHERE country.C_Code=countref.C_Code AND species.FamCode = families.FamCode AND countref.PAESE="Fr South Tr" AND country.SpecCode=species.SpecCode AND comnames.SpecCode=species.SpecCode AND country.Game=1

SELECT families.FamilyOrder, families.Family, species.Genus, species.Species, country.Status, comnames.ComName FROM fbapp.species, fbapp.country, fbapp.countref, fbapp.families, fbapp.comnames WHERE country.C_Code=countref.C_Code AND species.SpecCode=comnames.SpecCode AND species.SpecCode=country.SpecCode AND species.FamCode = families.FamCode AND countref.PAESE="Barbados" AND country.Importance="minor commercial"

SELECT species.Genus, species.Species, country.Status, species.UsedforAquaculture FROM fbapp.species, fbapp.country, fbapp.countref WHERE country.C_Code=countref.C_Code AND species.SpecCode = country.SpecCode AND countref.PAESE="Liberia" AND country.Aquaculture='commercial'

SELECT species.Genus, species.Species, country.Aquaculture, country.Status FROM fbapp.species, fbapp.country, fbapp.countref WHERE species.SpecCode = country.SpecCode AND country.C_Code=countref.C_Code AND countref.PAESE="US Virgin Is" AND species.UsedforAquaculture='commercial'

SELECT species.Genus, species.Species, country.Status, species.Aquarium FROM fbapp.species, fbapp.country, fbapp.countref WHERE species.SpecCode = country.SpecCode AND country.C_Code=countref.C_Code AND countref.PAESE="Juan Fern‡ndez" AND country.LiveExport='ornamental'
